  &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sometimes you will find an app opened but the icon is too small in the dock.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;solution&#34;&gt;
  Solution
  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#solution&#34;&gt;
    &lt;i class=&#34;fa fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can try this command in your terminal.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#586e75;background-color:#eee8d5;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;killall Dock
